data.description: This is a great home in town for sale that feels like a country home in Hardy, Arkansas.  This 3540 sq.ft. home has 3 bedrooms, 3 ½ baths.  The main section of the home was custom built by qualified architects, & has numerous unique features from the custom built kitchen to the custom walk in closets, plus it is handicap accessible. Solarium divides the Custom built home from the separate living space and garage.   This is a one of a kind Legacy property in the Rio Vista First subdivision; it has strictly enforced covenants & provides a common access point to the Spring River.
